Stable Diffusion Clothing Image Generator
This project generates AI-powered fashion images based on user-inputted details like gender, clothing type, material, sleeve type, and more. It utilizes Stable Diffusion for high-quality image generation.

🚀 Features
Generate AI images of outfits based on custom user input
Uses Stable Diffusion 2.1 for ultra-realistic outputs
Negative prompts to improve quality and avoid distortions
Saves images locally for easy access
📌 Installation
Clone the repository
sh
Copy
Edit
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/your-repo.git
cd your-repo
Install dependencies
sh
Copy
Edit
pip install -r requirements.txt
Run the script
sh
Copy
Edit
python generate_image.py
📝 Usage
Run the script and enter details (e.g., gender, clothing type, material).
The script generates an ultra-HD outfit image based on your input.
The image is saved as generated_image.png.
📂 Project Structure
bash
Copy
Edit
/your-repo
│── generate_image.py      # Main script for image generation
│── requirements.txt       # Dependencies
│── generated_images/      # Folder for storing images
│── README.md              # Project documentation
📌 Example Input
yaml
Copy
Edit
Enter gender: girl
Enter clothing type: lehenga
Enter material: silk
Enter sleeve type: puff sleeves
Enter neck type: sweetheart neck
Enter occasion: wedding
Enter background: palace
Enter extra features: golden embroidery
Enter primary color: red
🎨 Example Output
A high-quality AI-generated image of a red silk lehenga with puff sleeves, a sweetheart neck, and golden embroidery in a palace setting.

